# ShellSage üêö

ShellSage is your friendly command-line companion ‚Äî run any shell command with beautiful output formatting.


### Installation:
```bash
pip install shellsage-cli
```

### Usage:
```bash
shellsage "ls -la"
shellsage "ps aux | grep python"
shellsage "find . -name '*.py' -exec wc -l {} +"

